1. *Rade* na niskim temperaturama. (They work at low temperatures.)
2. Oni *rade* zajedno. (They are working together.)
3. Ona *rade* na tom projektu. (She is working on that project.)
4. *Radili* smo zajedno. (We worked together.)
5. Njegov brat *rade* u banki. (His brother works in a bank.)
6. Oni su *radili* svoj posao. (They were doing their job.)
7. *Radi* u toj kompaniji. (He works in that company.)
8. Oni su *radili* od ranog jutra. (They were working from early morning.)